---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

---

<Layout title="Uses - Sam Julien">
  <div class="mb-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Uses</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Last updated: March 2025</p>
  </div>
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <p>
      This is my <a href="https://uses.tech" target="_blank" class="text-brand hover:text-brand-dark">uses page</a>, a list of hardware, software, and tools I use on a daily basis. I'm always refining my setup to optimize for productivity and ergonomics.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">General hardware</h2>
 <ul>
 <li><a href="https://www.zsa.io/moonlander">Moonlander Keyboard</a> - Ergonomic split mechanical keyboard by ZSA</li>
 <li><a href="https://www.autonomous.ai/standing-desks/autonomous-desk-duospace">Autonomous White L-Shaped Standing Desk</a> - Ergonomic height-adjustable corner desk</li>
<li><a href="https://www.kensington.com/p/products/electronic-control-solutions/trackball-products/expert-mouse-wireless-trackball-2/">Kensington Expert Mouse Trackball</a> - Ergonomic wireless trackball mouse</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.hermanmiller.com/products/seating/office-chairs/aeron-chair/">Herman Miller Aeron Chair</a> - Ergonomic office chair</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Development tools</h2>
    <p>I write code daily in JavaScript and Python. This site is built with Astro. In addition to the usual tools like git, here are my favorite coding tools:</p>
    <ul>
       <li><a href="https://www.cursor.com/en">Cursor</a> - AI-powered code editor</li>
  <li><a href="https://codeium.com/windsurf">Windsurf</a> - AI agentic code editor by Codeium</li>
  <li><a href="https://workingcopy.app/">Working Copy</a> - Git client for iOS</li>
  <li><a href="https://getdrafts.com/">Drafts</a> - Text editor and automation tool for iOS and Mac</li>
  <li><a href="https://lmstudio.ai/">LM Studio</a> - Application for running large language models locally</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Productivity</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://ugmonk.com/pages/analog">Ugmonk Analog</a> - Physical productivity system</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.elgato.com/us/en/p/stream-deck-plus-black">Elgato Stream Deck</a> - Customizable control interface</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.elgato.com/us/en/p/stream-deck-pedal">Elgato Stream Deck Pedal</a> - Hands-free control accessory</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.studioneat.com/products/markone">Studio Neat Mark One</a> - Minimal, durable, retractable pen</li>
      <li><a href="https://obsidian.md/">Obsidian</a> - Knowledge base and note-taking application</li>
      <li><a href="https://whispermemos.com/">Whisper Memos</a> - Voice-to-text transcription iOS app</li>
  <li><a href="https://superwhisper.com/">Superwhisper</a> - AI-powered voice-to-text for macOS</li>
  <li><a href="https://setapp.com">Setapp</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://folivora.ai">BetterTouchTool</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.keyboardmaestro.com/main/">Keyboard Maestro</a> - Powerful Mac automation software</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Production</h2>
    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.elgato.com/us/en/p/wave-dx-dynamic-microphone">Elgato Wave DX</a> - Dynamic XLR microphone</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.elgato.com/us/en/p/wave-xlr">Elgato Wave XLR</a> - USB interface for XLR microphones</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.telestream.net/screenflow/overview.htm">ScreenFlow</a> - Video editing and screen recording software</li>
      <li><a href="https://getrecut.com/">Recut</a> - Automatic video editor that removes silence</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
      <p class="italic">
        Have questions about my setup? Feel free to reach out on <a href="https://x.com/samjulien" target="_blank" class="text-brand hover:text-brand-dark">X</a> or <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/samjulien/" target="_blank" class="text-brand hover:text-brand-dark">LinkedIn</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
